query:
-- Buscar etiqueta
SELECT 
  la.id as label_id,
  la.labelCode,
  la.productId as label_productId,
  p.sku as label_sku
FROM labelAssociations la
INNER JOIN products p ON la.productId = p.id
WHERE la.labelCode = '401460P22D10LB111'
LIMIT 1;

-- Buscar wave items da onda 1
SELECT 
  pwi.id as waveItem_id,
  pwi.productId as waveItem_productId,
  p.sku as waveItem_sku,
  pwi.batch
FROM pickingWaveItems pwi
INNER JOIN products p ON pwi.productId = p.id
WHERE pwi.waveId = 1
LIMIT 5;
